### Footnotes

<span id="fn_154"></span>[77:3](sbe20022.htm#fr_159.md) Anabhiratiyâ
pî*li*to attano aṅga*g*âtam *kh*indi. This anabhirati is constantly
referred to, and always as the result of falling in love, or in
connection with sexual desire.

